    <h2 id="level-23-level-24"><a href="#level-23-level-24">Level 23 → Level 24</a></h2>
    <p>
      Tiếp tục một bài về <code class="inline-code-block">crontab</code>
      , những bước đầu tiên thì như nhau thôi. Như thường lệ, ta sẽ đọc file
      <code class="inline-code-block">/usr/bin/cronjob_bandit24.sh</code>
    </p>
    <div class="code-block  ">
      <CodeCopy>
        <pre><code
            class="language-bash">{@html String.raw`<div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"><span class="token shebang important">#!/bin/bash</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"><span class="token assign-left variable">myname</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">&#36;(</span><span class="token function">whoami</span><span class="token variable">)</span></span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"><span class="token builtin class-name">cd</span> /var/spool/<span class="token variable">&#36;myname</span>/foo</div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"><span class="token builtin class-name">echo</span> <span class="token string">"Executing and deleting all scripts in /var/spool/<span class="token variable">&#36;myname</span>/foo:"</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"><span class="token keyword">for</span> <span class="token for-or-select variable">i</span> <span class="token keyword">in</span> * .*<span class="token punctuation">;</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"><span class="token keyword">do</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">    <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span> <span class="token string">"<span class="token variable">&#36;i</span>"</span> <span class="token operator">!=</span> <span class="token string">"."</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-a</span> <span class="token string">"<span class="token variable">&#36;i</span>"</span> <span class="token operator">!=</span> <span class="token string">".."</span> <span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">    <span class="token keyword">then</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">        <span class="token builtin class-name">echo</span> <span class="token string">"Handling <span class="token variable">&#36;i</span>"</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">        <span class="token assign-left variable">owner</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"<span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">&#36;(</span><span class="token function">stat</span> <span class="token parameter variable">--format</span> <span class="token string">"%U"</span> ./&#36;i<span class="token variable">)</span></span>"</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">        <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span> <span class="token string">"<span class="token variable">&#36;{owner}</span>"</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">"bandit23"</span> <span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token keyword">then</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">            <span class="token function">timeout</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-s</span> <span class="token number">9</span> <span class="token number">60</span> ./<span class="token variable">&#36;i</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">        <span class="token keyword">fi</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">        <span class="token function">rm</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-f</span> ./<span class="token variable">&#36;i</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">    <span class="token keyword">fi</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"><span class="token keyword">done</span></div></div>`}</code></pre>
