            class="language-bash">{@html String.raw`<div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"><span class="token shebang important">#!/bin/bash</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"><span class="token function">cat</span> /etc/bandit_pass/bandit24 <span class="token operator">></span> /tmp/tmp_ne/pw</div></div>`}</code></pre>
      </CodeCopy>
    </div>
    <p>
