      pincode từ 0000 đến 9999 để bruteforce thẳng, file đấy có thể tạo từ bash script như sau
    </p>
    <div class="code-block  ">
      <CodeCopy>
        <pre><code
            class="language-bash">{@html String.raw`<div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"><span class="token shebang important">#!/bin/bash</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"><span class="token keyword">for</span> <span class="token for-or-select variable">i</span> <span class="token keyword">in</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">..</span><span class="token number">9999</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"><span class="token keyword">do</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">            <span class="token builtin class-name">echo</span> VAfGXJ1PBSsPSnvsjI8p759leLZ9GGar <span class="token variable">&#36;i</span> <span class="token operator">>></span> no.txt</div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"><span class="token keyword">done</span></div></div>`}</code></pre>
      </CodeCopy>
    </div>
    <p>
